  "title": "Delicate Fluffy Norwegian Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A traditional Norwegian dish featuring tender lamb and fluffy texture, perfect for a comforting meal. This paleo-friendly recipe is also a great hangover cure.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
